{
  "id": "2652459548_2",
  "title": "她们在戈壁，过不荒凉的人生",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 165, 235);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n      澎湃新闻记者 陈蕾\n     </span>\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     在戈壁，时间就像长了腿，很容易在辽阔苍茫的荒漠与蓝天之间悄悄溜走。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     赶骆驼很花时间。牧民孟根其木格养了200多峰骆驼，18万亩的牧场上，她常跨着摩托车找骆驼、赶骆驼，“句句句句”地喊。有时找得困难，一晃就从白天到了黑夜。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     更花时间的是日复一日地在此坚守。十九年前初来戈壁，朝乐蒙花一身黄裙、踩一双高跟鞋。如今，快六十岁的她坐在小帐篷里守着羊群，一口一口吃着用小锅做的麻婆豆腐，时光爬上了她被风吹日晒的脸。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     她们是牧民，也是边民。边陲小镇马鬃山镇，这座位于河西走廊边缘的小镇，北与蒙古国接壤，是甘肃省酒泉市肃北蒙古族自治县的一块“飞地”，距酒泉市中心有4小时车程。全镇面积3.2万平方公里，相当于5倍上海市面积大小，但镇村常住人口仅500多人。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n  <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe js_wechannel_video_card js_wx_tap_highlight\" data-authiconurl=\"http://dldir1.qq.com/weixin/checkresupdate/internet_news_media_auth_icon_38887ee9f6fe4639904638b28745b3f8.png\" data-desc=\"马鬃山镇的面积，约等于5个上海。\n但三万多平方公里的戈壁，住着500多人，比骆驼还难得一见。\n电和公路到达这里，也不过十来年。\n马鬃山人习惯了被荒芜和寂寥包围。他们经年在戈壁深处，守着自家十几万亩的牧场，和风沙、干旱相处，和羊群、骆驼作伴。\n他们也格外渴望相逢。串个相隔两百公里的门，去朋友家帮忙修剪驼毛；组织一场家族敖包，六七十岁的老头老太们，唱一首蒙古长调，然后上场射箭摔跤。特别鸣谢@肃北融媒 @边防重镇马鬃山镇 \n#千亿扶持加码电商西进# #国境线上的祭敖包 #电商西进重新定义包邮区 #甘肃 #戈壁 #拼多多 #文旅\n\" data-feedcoverurl=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqz3Q09mMjFiaAXhjUN58HbPFoPehia5s9Taia8PibXk3R60lYcJ5T303AMtxXb3Y0Fm8CfBfroIlUibCsbSKnLHPGDwgA&amp;token=AxricY7RBHdWNYNYSFwLRqlbmYYgtwNdQzGTPhibqrJ7KQ0e560oXicHDcNO7HVgJx3TepllUfcM353FcbJs5LqxdvCK1SKCickUgN38AMDNAaDo17HGDe8yoMazQmshhoQ6FThxPALicFEjhSmoK59wrqyQuPRr8xWG5Hk9EAahJzwA&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=&amp;scene=2&amp;uzid=1\" data-feedfullcoverurl=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzsSCcygZ8y7E2EkrDt0mRMiajZCkZyXickc2qaMx91tW0ag4pZEIQDYn7dgcrTjStT8190yVj1NWEfMlrX6Uzxcicw&amp;token=2lt8WBSnjTl9lghQ9nZ7HeLibjricOgQibHynPg5iadQRPlg0QyZbAkSr0ERBJpQ7KlvU1XJS4t87NtAVkibAejuCGx6FwzyNhwKxAgETz7IBOSoOicrtWk54umyeSiaVY0zA99DxXqlCqdqtuJ4BOJibpzqnWDlWu5VwVtL18yHtFQFxeQ&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=&amp;scene=2&amp;uzid=1\" data-feedthumburl=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzXgkbxDJIf2OMVcy7pS7ks1B7MCRRVspsEmkqGMU5FnNicjhw3yiaryXfT7c1WYZIjSB8BSGBIze4XvQfTGzFl6fg&amp;token=ic1n0xDG6awicTMnBUIgmKlY86P6zFboZ6zTPJv7icu2H7fOzib5yArqic3UzbzEOZPRwU0JUqtG3OD0bpVPpAlHibFNcPhEUD0kYzGIItw2gnStZB8IuiaRF7iaHOStcr7XdcaT7ia0MiaKJwsbBzybajeOabWX2qSyiby7JJrxvUAKPweb9w&amp;idx=1&amp;bizid=1023&amp;dotrans=0&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=&amp;uzid=1\" data-flag=\"0\" data-headimgurl=\"http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/0nn3FBrD9a3p8JkxgttfvRKI2pt1RkOYx7icX9wtR2Xap8n4Tdoib3pg/0\" data-height=\"1080\" data-id=\"export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAZQQSS9vXRgAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPE4YJgLBNUQZeIzNPgMIvjylt2YsIhqWHCr0a5P0ht\" data-isnews=\"1\" data-likenum=\"1009\" data-nickname=\"澎湃新闻\" data-nonceid=\"6306991820180255037\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-type=\"video\" data-url=\"https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzsSCcygZ8y7E2EkrDt0mRMiajZCkZyXickc2qaMx91tW0ag4pZEIQDYn7dgcrTjStT8190yVj1NWEfMlrX6Uzxcicw&amp;token=2lt8WBSnjTl7X63bqy3qI0xNXNC6jzcaIudCcljcNvF0jsUhc7SxCyaHCSLmnNOSBeGOOs3LziaNINiaLVqfAAT4cFLmj3JBVh3zTQiaBZFrtJ4wxlHGicdJY7COMyYia3icx7S30QicUCJdrwicOzcic5dEzBUmmP7I2gezbzY1nYLyVyjs&amp;idx=1&amp;hy=SH&amp;m=&amp;scene=2&amp;uzid=1\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c7e48d19c0d4c90ce533b0772e1c08f4c6e0ce38be3ca98f63f23589@finder\" data-width=\"1920\">\n  </mp-common-videosnap>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     出品人：徐香 总监制：黄武锋、文若愚 导演：何惠子 撰稿：何惠子 统筹：张歆旎 制片：胡弘彪 剪辑：李国柱 视觉设计：牛嘉良 后期监制：龙景 制作：澎湃新闻·源深视频 鸣谢：中共肃北蒙古族自治县委宣传部\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     广阔的戈壁滩上，牧民在此放牧、守边，岁月淬炼出他们的坚韧。而这些年，随着通路、通电、通网，“兴边富民”的建设，新的变化在这片原始的土地悄然发生。与外界互通的时间和生活顺着网线逐渐被搭起。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 165, 235);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n      飞地深处的游牧牧民\n     </span>\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     每年三到五月是养驼大户孟根其木格正忙的时候：要换季了，她得给骆驼剪毛，帮助它们适应高温，还要惦记把驼毛卖出好价钱。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     她和丈夫找了四个工人，一起给骆驼剪毛。风一吹，黄沙四起往脸上扑来。44岁的孟根戴着帽子，用头巾、口罩把自己的脸包裹得严实。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-height=\"845\" data-imgfileid=\"100007296\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1267\" height=\"845\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/rM39QibdQCVCswcOVu9lZJzdjAsfQoUSnw2bgCcjLl9tDnXLR4g9aibGRM9dtZ1vscna1kbX9kxTuYo5h5Sm8ClA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style='box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;height: auto;display: block;max-width: 1080px;width: 1080px;margin-top: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft Yahei\", sans-serif;font-size: 38px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;' width=\"1267\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     阳光下，充满好奇心的骆驼正排着队望向前方。（澎湃新闻 胡弘彪|摄）\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     一般情况下，骆驼是温顺的，人靠近，它们会垂着长睫毛，用一双大眼睛看着你，跟着你行进的方向慢慢晃自己的脑袋。吃起草来，它们的下颌一左一右来回摆动。它们总是低眉，一副与世无争的样子。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     一峰峰骆驼走进孟根为它们设置的护栏里。在那里，它们排队站着望向前方，任人用长剪刀顺着它们皮毛的肌理“咔嚓咔嚓”。浅棕色的骆驼伏在孟根身前，头扭到后面。孟根单膝蹲下，黑白色的运动卫衣下，一副紫手套麻利地挥舞着剪刀。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     遇到脾气大的、犟的骆驼，剪毛就没这么轻松。它们会踢会跪，踢你一裤腿尘土，或朝你吐一口唾沫。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-height=\"845\" data-imgfileid=\"100007295\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1267\" height=\"845\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/rM39QibdQCVCswcOVu9lZJzdjAsfQoUSnsAEl91VNGsFicmA8CQYoV3JBhy2Mnh204e9YOODwXuaOMkCmRhIMbuA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style='box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;height: auto;display: block;max-width: 1080px;width: 1080px;margin-top: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft Yahei\", sans-serif;font-size: 38px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;' width=\"1267\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     牧场里，工人正在给骆驼剪毛（澎湃新闻 胡弘彪|摄）\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     太阳一点点移下山岗，戈壁被照出暖调的金色，快要21点，孟根和工友们即将结束一天的劳作。围栏铁丝上留着一缕一缕的骆驼毛，风一吹，毛就像芦苇一样顺风而晃。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     孟根是在牧区长大的蒙古族人。六年前从母亲手中接管牧场后，她打理着母亲和弟弟名下的骆驼，六年来从80多峰养到了200多峰。除此之外，她还放马放羊，养猫养狗。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     小时候，孩子们被父母问及将来谁去上学、谁去放羊，她主动请缨放牧，被母亲拒绝，说她是家里老大,该去上学。但孟根很想放牧，她觉得放牧开心，也觉得父母需要帮手，读书到四年级便停下了。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     她有好多话要和动物说，小小的她骑着马问马，“背着我你累吗？”太阳落下又升起，她看着家里的马和骆驼一日日长大、繁衍后代。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-height=\"845\" data-imgfileid=\"100007294\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1267\" height=\"845\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/rM39QibdQCVCswcOVu9lZJzdjAsfQoUSnbQ2JZoajZpLFBQGFxdP4l2ZIyz9jR9I4rgBehSfic8v3qGLGxrvIOUA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style='box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;height: auto;display: block;max-width: 1080px;width: 1080px;margin-top: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft Yahei\", sans-serif;font-size: 38px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;' width=\"1267\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     孟根悉心照顾着牧场里的骆驼，日复一日。（澎湃新闻 胡弘彪|摄）\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     她家有一峰骆驼是元月产的，和普通的二三月产的不一样。孟根很宝贝它，在它出生后，怕它冻着抱到了房子里。孟根的母亲给它做了蓝白色的小马甲，让小骆驼的四个蹄子露出来。现在这峰骆驼已有七八岁，很亲近人，身上哪都让人摸。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     孟根是18万亩牧场的主人，日常戴着头盔骑摩托车驶过戈壁，在石砾、黄沙上飞驰，每天最记挂的就是自己的动物们，在戈壁上数骆驼，数量对了，心也安了。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     快六十岁的牧民朝乐蒙花，她的生活也有着如此原始的生命力，和孟根一样逐水草而生，一年四季待在马鬃山镇不同的牧场。不过和原住民孟根不同，她从内蒙古来。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     打小在牧区长大的朝乐蒙花，在内蒙古县城读书、工作后，九十年代了解到肃北县也有蒙古族，很是好奇，先在肃北县县城做手工艺品、做马头琴，2006年，她来到了马鬃山镇。苍茫的黑戈壁、草场留住了她，她想在这片人烟稀少的地方闯荡、放羊。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-height=\"845\" data-imgfileid=\"100007293\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1267\" height=\"845\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/rM39QibdQCVCswcOVu9lZJzdjAsfQoUSnWneoibJXYuibCvcJdRx1stfrLfCP0pM5mdiatdnIRDiaan8TJicAYrQfqhQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style='box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;height: auto;display: block;max-width: 1080px;width: 1080px;margin-top: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft Yahei\", sans-serif;font-size: 38px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;' width=\"1267\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     在戈壁上哼着歌放羊，是朝乐蒙花每天最喜欢做的事。（澎湃新闻 胡弘彪|摄）\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     她还记得自己第一次在戈壁上见到狼，吓得半边脸都麻了；也记得有天下雨，她怕打雷，抱头坐在地上，很多羊围着自己转。狼追着她的羊，羊到处跑，她哭着鼻子找羊。但困难没有打倒这个有着铁一般意志的女人。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     朝乐蒙花还是喜欢游牧，觉得自由自在，放牧十几年，她说夏天是放羊最好的时候，骑着摩托吹着风，走得快快的，“唱个歌多舒服啊”。她喜欢远离纷扰，在戈壁上安静地自发记录蒙古族的俗语、歇后语。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 165, 235);font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n      在戈壁守望远方\n     </span>\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     马鬃山镇这些年的变化，朝乐蒙花都历历在目。2014年，马鬃山苏木（来源自蒙古语сум，属乡级行政区）通乡油路正式开工建设。通路后通电又通信号，她的夏季牧场旁矗立着高高的信号塔。2017年，国家西部大开发交通要道京新高速公路通车。2021年，马鬃山镇被正式列入国家第一批“兴边富民行动中心城镇”建设试点单位。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     人为建设为牧民安家立业提供保障。然而，自然的挑战依然严峻。马鬃山在蒸发量高达3000多毫米的同时，年降水量不到100毫米。这里属于荒漠气候，缺水。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     孟根说，尤其这五年来愈发干旱，缺水也缺自然草。缺草就要人工买苜蓿，这些草料比不上自然草的营养价值，骆驼这些年生病比以前多了，拉肚子、憋尿、不吃草，牧民只能请大夫，了解更多的信息以适应外界环境的变化。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     而牧场上骆驼和人的用水需求，需要靠掘井。孟根的牧场挖了三口井了，只有两个水泵。6月的一天，孟根的新水泵到了，她骑着摩托车去镇上取来快递。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-height=\"1000\" data-imgfileid=\"100007297\" data-ratio=\"1.4992503748125936\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"667\" data-width=\"667\" height=\"1000\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/rM39QibdQCVCswcOVu9lZJzdjAsfQoUSnxC0GvEAV8ibUuc0y9taSOrelvfBv3XLFYAMxKRRjyfVOiaBBM3RZbFKQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style='box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;height: auto;display: block;max-width: 1080px;width: 1080px;margin-top: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft Yahei\", sans-serif;font-size: 38px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;' width=\"667\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     孟根正拆开从拼多多上网购回来的发电机。（澎湃新闻记者 陈蕾|摄）\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     孟根记得，自从2016年左右，马鬃山镇通了信号，能用上微信，她开始学会网络购物。在这之前，她只会原始的方式，生活用品去镇上买，大概离牧区半小时路程。如果是骆驼饲料这种镇上买不到的东西，得乘车去玉门，路上行程3到5个小时。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     现在牧场需要的一些工具，比如发电机、绳子、袋子，她都可以直接网上买了，而且更便宜。新水泵是在拼多多上买的，拼多多包邮的商品会送到镇上的代收点，她有空就可以去拿。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     这样的便捷背后得益于拼多多近年来大力推动的“电商西进”行动。2024年9月，拼多多在此前首创中转集运模式，大幅降低物流成本的基础上，又率先宣布所有商家在西藏、甘肃、宁夏、内蒙古等偏远地区产生的物流中转费由平台“买单”。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     今年4月，拼多多又推出“千亿扶持”计划，未来三年内拟投入资金、流量等资源超过1000亿元人民币，加码高质量电商生态建设，全力构建用户、商家及平台多方共赢的商业生态。其中，引领更多优质商品加快向西部地区供应是“千亿扶持”重点倾斜资源支持的专项之一。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     也正因如此，像孟根一样的牧民们的生活需求正一步步被看到、被认真对待。公开数据显示，2024年，全国社会消费品零售总额同比增长3.5%，西藏、宁夏、内蒙古、甘肃等省份均超过全国平均水平。拼多多平台数据显示，过去一年，西部地区订单实现双位数增长。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-height=\"714\" data-imgfileid=\"100007298\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1269\" height=\"714\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/rM39QibdQCVCswcOVu9lZJzdjAsfQoUSnWZibmKHGYPIDyrtVVfePPKsibvDIYFrlD0ic0XG42sxuNKlzuvInOPdmg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style='box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;height: auto;display: block;max-width: 1080px;width: 1080px;margin-top: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft Yahei\", sans-serif;font-size: 38px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;' width=\"1269\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     牧民正用摩托将骆驼赶回牧场。（澎湃新闻记者 何惠子|摄）\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     在拼多多的支持下，孟根的一次次实惠网购实现了。随着她对新水泵的一通操作，水管的水向外涌出。她先清洗了骆驼的水槽，洁白的水花涌向水槽时，清凉的生命力也向干旱的戈壁涌来。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     相近的时间内，朝乐蒙花在马鬃山镇拿到了她的快递，一顶绿色帐篷。日薄西山，羊该回圈了，她骑着摩托把羊赶了回来，撑起在拼多多购得的帐篷，坐在里面唱起了歌。悠扬的歌声回荡在山头。她看向远方，鬓角的头发被风拂起。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-height=\"1000\" data-imgfileid=\"100007299\" data-ratio=\"1.4992503748125936\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"667\" data-width=\"667\" height=\"1000\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/rM39QibdQCVCswcOVu9lZJzdjAsfQoUSnCiaFwJc6zGFNbPCjcNYNt0KzdZuQdPHauRzXNo2W1G1DhWmt4nZr9CA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style='box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;height: auto;display: block;max-width: 1080px;width: 1080px;margin-top: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft Yahei\", sans-serif;font-size: 38px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 1080px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;' width=\"667\"/>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" textstyle=\"\">\n     拼多多的电商西进让朝乐蒙花网购生活用品变得简单。（澎湃新闻记者 陈蕾|摄）\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     不用掏高昂的运费，不用坐车去玉门去酒泉，不用等待十天半个月，在茫茫的黑戈壁上，物流通达提高了时间的使用效率。孟根和朝乐蒙花更方便地触及到了生活所需，也触及到了马鬃山镇以外的世界。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     孟根自己未踏足过甘肃、青海以外的地方。她对马鬃山镇的土地和骆驼怀有深厚的感情，“城市偶尔去一趟，有新鲜的感觉，待两三天就很着急想回家。”\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     她把对外界的期冀寄托在女儿身上。她24岁的女儿，从小被带出马鬃山镇读书，即将毕业想考军队文职，孟根期待女儿如愿。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style='color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;'>\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n     而孟根还要在这里照顾她的骆驼。戈壁是孟根的家，只有在家，她才感觉心里“宽宽的”。对她来说，守在家乡的每一天，都印证着马鬃山站站台外那句醒目的蓝色标语：只有荒凉的戈壁，没有荒凉的人生。\n    </span>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"display: none;\">\n  <mp-style-type data-value=\"3\">\n  </mp-style-type>\n </p>\n</div>\n",
